ers change scripts every time we make a release.  So, don't put package-x.y.z in installed path.  Either:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>pull back to x.y (i.e., imply compatibility across patchlevels for given major/minor)\nOR</li>\n<li>don't embed path at all</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Same goes for Gazebo.</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "assignee": {"display_name": "Brian Gerkey", "uuid": "{3d8b5763-9dad-4be7-85c2-a7ab6cd49173}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B3d8b5763-9dad-4be7-85c2-a7ab6cd49173%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B3d8b5763-9dad-4be7-85c2-a7ab6cd49173%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "https://avatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.net/557058:2e35028e-9ad8-4d6a-a3a5-275159a304a9/5fa9ec73-0fec-4860-a202-e34ae23b6a12/128"}}, "nickname": "Brian Gerkey", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:2e35028e-9ad8-4d6a-a3a5-275159a304a9"}, "state": "resolved", "version": null, "edited_on": null, "created_on": "2012-10-13T02:21:45.518993+00:00", "milestone": null, "updated_on": "2012-10-15T17:36:48.168781+00:00", "type": "issue", "id": 4}